latestIgtvVideos.title: A-Z
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
I’m super proud mommy as my little Aavya has learned A-Z, with full confidence she brings her book & will start repeating A-Z. It is a proud moment to see a little baby saying everything with great confidence. 

The key to learning is to keep on repeating the same book on a regular basis & kids learn so fast. The best part is she feels that she will receive a bunch of claps from mommy when she recited every thing 💓

Patience & time is the key with your kids & they can learn everything 💓

latestIgtvVideos.caption:

In this recipe I have used the famous & my favourite pancake mix from @bettycrockerindia

I get my fresh blueberries from @bigbasketcom & also all my other ingredients 🤍

Cocomelon Rhymes 💚
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
As I have always mentioned that learning should be fun especially for toddlers at an such an early stage, where they are discovering every bit. I found this channel @cocomelon_official . It is a great channel to make learning fun for your toddlers, Aavya has learnt so many words and rhymes just watching this channel. The creative way that they put on to describe each rhyme is so so great. 

I guess I sing half of their poems word by word with music. 

So mommies if you want your toddlers to have a screen time which comes with a little learning I guess you should subscribe to their channel @cocomelon_official 💚
